---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<p
  class="hero-badge mb-8 inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full border border-brand-300/60 bg-white/70 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-brand-700 backdrop-blur-sm"
>
  <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
    <span
      class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-accent opacity-60"
    ></span>
    <span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
  </span>
  v0.1 · BroadcastChannel nativo
</p>

<h1
  class="hero-headline font-display text-[clamp(2.75rem,6.5vw,5rem)] leading-[0.95] font-extrabold tracking-[-0.03em] text-brand-900"
>
  <span class="block">Sincroniza</span>
  <span class="block">
    tus
    <span class="relative mx-1 inline-block">
      <span class="relative z-10">pestañas</span>
      <span
        class="absolute -inset-x-2 -inset-y-1 z-0 -skew-x-2 rounded-sm bg-brand-300/50"
      ></span>
    </span>
  </span>
  <span class="mt-1 block text-brand-500"> en tiempo real </span>
</h1>

<p
  class="hero-subhead mt-8 max-w-xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-brand-700/90 lg:text-2xl lg:leading-relaxed"
>
  Conecta el estado entre pestañas al instante. Sin servidor, sin WebSockets,
  sin configuración extra.
</p>

<div class="hero-ctas mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
  <a
    id="hero-cta"
    href="/docs/getting-started/introduccion"
    class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-md bg-brand-600 px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-on-accent shadow-[0_10px_36px_-6px_var(--indigo-glow)] transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-px hover:bg-brand-500 hover:shadow-[0_14px_44px_-6px_var(--indigo-glow-hover)] active:translate-y-0 active:shadow-[0_6px_20px_-6px_var(--indigo-glow-active)] motion-reduce:hover:translate-y-0"
  >
    Empezar ahora
    <Icon
      name="lucide:arrow-right"
      class="h-5 w-5 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 motion-reduce:group-hover:translate-x-0"
    />
  </a>

  <a
    href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/tabus-js"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noreferrer"
    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-brand-300/70 bg-white/60 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-brand-700 backdrop-blur-sm transition-colors hover:border-brand-400 hover:bg-white hover:text-brand-900"
  >
    <Icon name="simple-icons:npm" class="h-5 w-5" />
    npm
  </a>
</div>
